SQL_STMT_U.val:
Select tot.break_date from ( --Historic performance data: SELECT hb.calc_date AS break_date FROM pc_historic_amounts ha INNER JOIN pc_category hc ON hc.id = ha.pcca_id INNER JOIN pc_historic_portfolio_base hb ON hb.id = ha.phpb_id INNER JOIN performance_report hr ON hr.id = hb.pere_id WHERE hb.calc_date >= to_date(~1, 'YYYYMMDD') AND hr.ppr_id = ~2 AND hc.code = 204 GROUP BY hb.calc_date HAVING -- In Order to not include dates for which rounding differences cause the sum to differ from zero, -- only sums smaller than -1 or bigger than 1 are included: abs(SUM(ha.value)) > 1
UNION --Regular performance data: SELECT b.transaction_date AS break_date FROM pc_transaction_amount a INNER JOIN pc_category c ON c.id = a.pcca_id INNER JOIN pc_transaction_base b ON b.id = a.pctb_id INNER JOIN performance_report r ON r.id = b.pere_id WHERE b.transaction_date >= to_date(~1, 'YYYYMMDD') AND r.ppr_id = ~2 AND c.code = 204 GROUP BY b.transaction_date HAVING -- In Order to not include dates for which rounding differences cause the sum to differ from zero, -- only sums smaller than -1 or bigger than 1 are included: abs(SUM(a.amount)) > 1 ) tot order by tot.break_date desc
